      "created": "2019-06-26T16:22:22.982+0000",
      "description": "SchedulerQueueManager is currently an interface aka a protocol-only type. As seen in the codebase, each scheduler implements the queue configuration and management stuff over and over. If we convert it into a base concrete class with simple implementation of hierarchical queue system (as in Fair and Capacity schedulers), pluggable schedulers may be developed more easily.",
